      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:4:38:7",
      "text": [
        " كَانَ أَمِيرُ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ ( عليه السلام ) يَقُولُ إِذَا اسْوَدَّتِ الثَّنِيَّةُ جُعِلَ فِيهَا الدِّيَةُ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, from Ali Bin Al Hakam, or someone else, from Aban, from one of his companions, ",
          "Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> has said: ‘Amir Al-Momineen<sup>asws</sup> was saying: ‘When the incisors blacken, the wergild would be applicable regarding it’."
        ]
      }
